    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tie hangers or other hangers that incorporate a coil or other mechanism to allow small amounts of vertical or lateral movement, used to suspend ceilings, floors, in bridges, and for other construction uses.</Note_Text>
